<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَسَمِعْتَ فِي التَّارِيخِ عَنْ قَوْمٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَعَوْا لِلذُّلِّ أَلْقَوْا عِزَّهُمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَرَأَيْتَ كَيْفَ الآنَ صَارَ النِّفْطُ أَغْلَى مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَنَا شَاهِدٌ بَيْنَ الْوَرَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>النِّفْطُ أَغْلَى مِنْ دَمِكْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مُذْ يَوْمِ صَارَ الْحَاكِمُ الطَّاغُوتُ عِنْدَكُمُ الإِلَهْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>هَلْ يُسْأَلَنْ عَنْ فِعْلِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوْ فَعْلَةٍ مِنْ أَهْلِهِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ذَاكَ الْجُنُونْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالْكُلُّ يُسْأَلُ عَنْ خَوَاطِرِ نَفْسِهِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَنْ حُلْمِهِ فِي نَوْمِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالْكُلُّ يَنْعَمُ فِي هِبَاتِ يَدَيْهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>